Package com.rb.nonbiz.collections

Interface IndexableDoubleDataStore2D<R,​C>

All Known Implementing Classes:
ImmutableDoubleIndexableArray2D, MutableDoubleIndexableArray2D, RBIndexableMatrix, RBIndexableSquareMatrix
public interface IndexableDoubleDataStore2D<R,​C>
A 2-dimensional collection of doubles that's not bound to a particular implementation: implementers of this interface could be using e.g. a 2-d double array, or a Colt (linear algebra library) DoubleMatrix2D, or anything else.
